ts to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom radio trait.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker itself does no have any defined accessiiblity value, label or identifier ; it remains in the users hands to define which one will be used.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"However if defined in the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioPickerData","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" the items inside the picker will have such accessibility identifiers.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Forbidden by design","anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" in both an error situation and a read only state.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The design system does not allow to have ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" in both an error situation and a disabled state.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The design system does not allow to have ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" in both a read only and a disabled state.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define the elements to display in radio buttons using OUDSRadioPickerData.","    \/\/ This object has the same properties as the OUDSRadioItem,","    \/\/ and some of them are optional withdefault values set","    var someDataToPopulate: [OUDSRadioPickerData<String>] {","        [","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_1\",","                                        label: \"Virgin Holy Lava\",","                                        extraLabel: \"Very spicy\",","                                        description: \"No alcohol, only tasty flavors\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"flame\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_2\",","                                        label: \"IPA beer\",","                                        description: \"From Brewdog company\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"dog.fill\")),","","            OUDSRadioPickerData<String>(tag: \"Choice_3\",","                                        label: \"Mineral water\",","                                        icon: Image(systemName: \"waterbottle.fill\")),","        ]","    }","","    \/\/ Prepare the selection, with a value previously selected","    \/\/ Use the data and the binding for the picker.","    @State var selection: String = \"Choice_1\"","","    \/\/ Here the picker is vertical","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection, radios: someDataToPopulate)","","    \/\/ The picker can apply some settings to all its radio buttons.","    \/\/ It can be also horitzontal with a scroll indicator.","    \/\/ Here all the the radio buttons are in read only mode and use reversed layout.","    OUDSRadioPicker(selection: $selection,","                    radios: someDataToPopulate,","                    isReversed: true,","                    isReadOnly: true,","                    placement: .horitzontal(true))"],"type":"codeListing"},{"level":2,"text":"Design documentation","anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"There is no online specification as this component is not an official OUDS one","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Theme rendering","anchor":"Theme-rendering","type":"heading"},{"level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioPicker_Orange","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Orange Compact","anchor":"Orange-Compact","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioPicker_OrangeCompact","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Sosh","anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioPicker_Sosh","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":3,"text":"Wireframe","anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_radioPicker_Wireframe","type":"image"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"style":"note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since","type":"aside"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"A picker allowing to expose several radio buttons and choose only one within the others.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Each radio button contains a “tag”, i.e. a supposed to be unique value.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The picker will expose the choosen value through this “tag”.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"It has also some configuration elements which will override the one applied to nested ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadioItem"},{"text":" (divider, read only and error mode, layout and outlined)","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSR